title: Halo Audio Books 1 - 5 at 64Kbps.
description:
Halo Audio Books 1 - 5 at 64Kbps. 

Book 1: The Fall of Reach 
Book 2: The Flood 
Book 3: First Strike 
Book 4: Ghosts of Onyx 
Book 5: Contact Harvest. 

The bitrate is set at 64Kbps because, in my opinion, that is fine for spoken word and it helps keep the file size down so I can share these excellent books. Remember, support the authors and buy the books.
